Puffer Jacket Boys

Mint

Join us and Puff Up the world. 1 Puffer Jacket Boy costs 0.08 ETH- Which grants you full access to all of the Members' benefits.

Enter Club

Puffer Jacket Boys strive to help fight global issues

Puffer Jacket Boys are a collection of 10,000 rarity based digital collectibles with the aim to build a community that helps out the world. We refer to our NFT holders as Puffer Jacket Boys or Members. Each Member has the ability to choose & vote monthly on which charity the royalties charity funds(*) will go to, as well as get access to member exclusive benefits.

What's it like being one of the 'Jacket Boys'?

As a Puffer Jacket Boy holder you are a part of a community that seeks to help out others. For the first year we aim to tackle a different global issue each month by donating the Royalties Charity Funds(*) to different charity organizations. As a Member you will have the option to choose and vote on which charity the charity funds go to, as well as receive access to the Puffer Jacket Club where you can get to know all of the other Puffer Jacket Boys.

The Royalties Charity Fund

The Royalties Charity Fund is a monthly amount of ETH that will be donated to a charity organization based on the monthly voting of the Puffer Jacket Boys Members. For those who are in the world of crypto- it's like a DAO with the soul purpose of donating to charity. We plan on selling 10,000 NFTs (100 NFTs will be held back for future events), each costing 0.08 ETH on mint. From that point on we will be donating money to a different charity organization each month. From the profits of the initial sale we will create the Royalties Charity Funds(*)- which is 1.9% of all second-market sales royalties (3.1% additional royalties go to maintenance costs as well as the Puffer Jacket Boys Crew, adding up to 5% royalties).
FYI: NFT royalties are a percentage of profits taken from each transaction made with an NFT (for example: a PJB is sold on secondary market for 1ETH , then 0.00152ETH (1.9%) goes to the Royalties Charity Fund.
On release day, since there will be no transaction fees on mint, we will donate 50ETH from the pure profits we make. Meaning, on release day we hopefully reach 100,000$ in donations (if ETH crushes heavily we will match it back up to 100 grand lmao). From then on we will donate monthly to a charity chosen and voted on by the Puffer Jacket Boys (NFT holders / members). It's important to mention that this is not the only benefit of being a member- being a member also grants you perks such as the ones mentioned in the road map.

Team...

GUYBYNIGHT. ex-game developer, self taught graphic designer and sleep lover. I designed & generated all of the attributes, put together the smart contract with the help of thirdweb, and created this website all by myself. Yes, this is indeed- a one man operation. I've been working on this project for the past year and I can't wait to share it. I should also probably mention that as far as one man operations go, I do have a crew that I've assembled leading up to the release to help me manage the project & community as well as to keep things in check, But as far as NFT making goes... from designing characters, to smart-contract assemblage- it's all me baby

Special surprises to come in the future. guybynight, signing off.

FAQs
Where is the Royalties Charity Fund held?
How are the 10,000 Puffer Jacket Boys distributed?
7,875: Public sale minting of up to 2 mints per wallet 2,000: Whitelist of up to 2 mints per wallet 125: held back for roadmap plans, future collaborations, marketing, and advisors.
Is there an allow/whitelist?
Indeed, to get in the early minting allow list you must be visibly active / show interest in the project, join the discord and follow our twitter to see how you could enter... allow list caps at 2,000 spots & each person gets up to 2 early mints.
Is there a discord?
Yes, you can join by pressing the discord logo at the top of the page or right above the FAQs, however, note that this discord is for pre-release & general communication purposes only, and is not the Members community discord- which is NFT an gated server, meaning you must be a NFT holder to enter.
Will Puffer Jacket Boys be revealed right away?
Yes, you will immediately know what your new puffer friend looks like!
What intellectual property rights do PFB holders receive?
Owners of Puffer Jacket Boys will have full commercial art rights for the Puffer Jacket Boy they own. Full details coming soon (prior to launch).
